      <div class="about-text">
        <p>I am an academician, researcher, and mentor with a deep commitment to uncovering the intersection of <strong>marketing strategy, technology, and human behaviour</strong> in evolving business landscapes.</p>
        <p>Currently serving as <strong>Assistant Professor at CHRIST (Deemed to be University)</strong>, Bengaluru, I bring over 14 years of rich teaching experience spanning institutions across Andhra Pradesh and beyond, combined with industry-oriented research and placement expertise.</p>
